#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/Rd/index.rst:2
#: 02332e00a32a436893633574c602753f
msgid "雷达模组系列"
msgstr "Radar Module Series"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/Rd/index.rst:16
#: 921d3d87df8f4d75ada807146a615c2a
msgid "Rd-01模组的上位机以及搭建环境在哪儿获取？"
msgstr ""
"Where can I obtain the host computer software and environment setup for "
"the Rd-01 module?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/Rd/index.rst:17
#: ce181bda905e40218839ce856e526aba
msgid ""
"资料获取链接： `参考链接  <https://docs.ai-thinker.com/radar>`__ 开发环境以及上位机使用见博文： "
"`参考链接  <https://blog.csdn.net/Boantong_/article/details/130235376>`__"
msgstr ""
"Data download link: `Reference link <https://docs.ai-"
"thinker.com/radar>`__ For the development environment and host computer "
"software usage, please refer to the blog post: `Reference link "
"<https://blog.csdn.net/Boantong_/article/details/130235376>`__"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/Rd/index.rst:23
#: dee476f45d3b49f29fa51a4bf2cf35d9
msgid "Rd-01模组二次开发资料中，哪些是蓝牙那边的资料？"
msgstr ""
"In the secondary development materials of the Rd-01 module, which "
"materials are related to Bluetooth?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/Rd/index.rst:24
#: 4fe045c0e76f44149f35fe1ac27d3a40
msgid "SDK中的Ai-Thinker-WB2子模块中application下Bluetooth即为蓝牙相关用例。"
msgstr ""
"In the SDK, the Bluetooth-related examples are under "
"application/Bluetooth in the Ai-Thinker-WB2 submodule."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/Rd/index.rst:27
#: 548794fe0e884e5d85dc2742cff33a07
msgid "Rd-01模组能接入天猫精灵平台么？"
msgstr "Can the Rd-01 module be connected to the Tmall Genie platform?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/Rd/index.rst:28
#: f3a228e77d5348308ab362f6903036ec
msgid "不能。"
msgstr "No."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/Rd/index.rst:31
#: 325f57dd42004890941c4828484815fd
msgid "请问：Rd-01模组可以用arduino做开发吗？"
msgstr "Can the Rd-01 module be developed with Arduino?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/Rd/index.rst:32
#: b97b45b828da43dcb6d09957625f0d4a
msgid "不支持。"
msgstr "Not supported."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/Rd/index.rst:35
#: 2f477efaec70428b8c400a657157b1c0
msgid "Rd-01雷达模组可以监测出空间中人的数量吗，最多可以监测到几个人"
msgstr ""
"Can the Rd-01 radar module detect the number of people in a space? What "
"is the maximum number of people it can detect?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/Rd/index.rst:36
#: a14da668ef9844bf98f98e59b322592f
msgid "可以监测人的数量，需做二次开发实现，最多能监测到多少个人得看代码处理逻辑"
msgstr ""
"It can detect the number of people, but secondary development is "
"required. The maximum number of people that can be detected depends on "
"the code processing logic."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/Rd/index.rst:39
#: 3a1ad133c8224bc4be0ed5708b9cd560
msgid "Rd-01模块探测角度可调吗"
msgstr "Can the detection angle of the Rd-01 module be adjusted?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/Rd/index.rst:40
#: 353b21bf9886492f88a2420b8d534bfd
msgid "模块不可以调整探测角度"
msgstr "The detection angle of the module cannot be adjusted."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/Rd/index.rst:43
#: 5601894fdd53419895db1994c2861f8d
msgid "Rd-01模块上面有人体感应芯片吗"
msgstr "Does the Rd-01 module have a human presence sensing chip?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/Rd/index.rst:44
#: c57aaaa1526e49f7b77cf36531f35353
msgid "有，这款模组是由WIFI+BLE+雷达芯片组成的，可以进行人体感应"
msgstr ""
"Yes. This module consists of Wi-Fi + BLE + radar chip and can perform "
"human presence sensing."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/Rd/index.rst:47
#: 008697f5e31f40619686b22a8f083fc3
msgid "Rd-01雷达模组不接WIFI天线能否使用"
msgstr "Can the Rd-01 radar module be used without connecting the Wi-Fi antenna?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/Rd/index.rst:48
#: 98b2df49845343989bc18e93dc7c5641
msgid "模块上雷达芯片的天线是板载的，可以使用雷达功能"
msgstr ""
"The antenna of the radar chip on the module is onboard, so the radar "
"function can be used."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/Rd/index.rst:51
#: 563785e51d67414494953e4cc359bcea
msgid "Rd-01模块可以感应多远距离，安装在空调内合适吗"
msgstr ""
"How far can the Rd-01 module sense? Is it suitable to install inside an "
"air conditioner?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/Rd/index.rst:52
#: 298e3d8ec820422d982ebd4e1229dcc2
msgid "感应距离5米，可安装在空调内进行使用"
msgstr ""
"The sensing distance is 5 meters. It can be installed inside an air "
"conditioner for use."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/Rd/index.rst:55
#: 67f6fe3f5d4b4492b0689fc6fef8ba70
msgid "Rd-01模块能检测到静止的人吗"
msgstr "Can the Rd-01 module detect a stationary person?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/Rd/index.rst:56
#: 099d9ca0334a4d8ab7435bbcbd8a0fa9
msgid "模块可实现高灵敏度的人体存在状态感应，识别运动和静止状态下的人体"
msgstr ""
"The module can achieve high-sensitivity human presence sensing and "
"identify humans in both moving and stationary states."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/Rd/index.rst:59
#: 42718f8001b44a1ca959e63db7502379
msgid "请问Rd-01可以按照WB2的AT指令实现组网么?"
msgstr "Can Rd-01 implement networking according to WB2 AT commands?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/Rd/index.rst:60
#: e4513fb0dd71492b9faa6454a0ada8dd
msgid "不可以，雷达驱动与AT固件是两套东西"
msgstr "No. The radar driver and AT firmware are two separate things."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/Rd/index.rst:63
#: 96c6a7e2591846cfad645072dce5413e
msgid "请问雷达的最短检测距离是？"
msgstr "What is the minimum detection distance of the radar?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/Rd/index.rst:64
#: 6c98711285b64eeab86512d77e8e0db5
msgid "0.75米；"
msgstr "0.75 meters."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/Rd/index.rst:67
#: 15895ef687d3467eb9dd94b034fa17ab
msgid "Rd-01模组可以刷esphome固件吗"
msgstr "Can the Rd-01 module be flashed with ESPHome firmware?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/Rd/index.rst:68
#: b94fd7e361e24e46912591d3e7b4e0b5
msgid "不可以刷，内部芯片方案不同，Rd-01模组使用的是BL602系列芯片，并非ESP系列芯片"
msgstr ""
"No. The internal chip solution is different. The Rd-01 module uses the "
"BL602 series chip, not an ESP series chip."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/Rd/index.rst:71
#: 618464e087ad48f197bb78d123f60db5
msgid "雷达系列模组能区分物体和人体吗"
msgstr "Can the radar module series distinguish between objects and people?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/Rd/index.rst:72
#: 035ed87f388047e991e1b6761d08c02e
msgid "不能区分，仅支持监测是否有人无人"
msgstr "No. It only supports detecting whether someone is present or absent."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/Rd/index.rst:75
#: a5428fce0db64bf390d7b2e5738645d0
msgid "Rd-01雷达模组可以监测人体心跳和呼吸吗"
msgstr "Can the Rd-01 radar module detect human heartbeat and breathing?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/Rd/index.rst:76
#: 359cf77ff5694412919f4ba535c5488a
msgid "不可以监测心跳和呼吸，模组是可感知区域内是否有运动或者微动的人体"
msgstr ""
"No. It cannot detect heartbeat or breathing. The module can sense whether"
" there is a moving or slightly moving human body in the area."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/Rd/index.rst:79
#: a3899e3294bd42a182581c3fe20ceff3
msgid "雷达24g和10g在性能上有什么差异吗"
msgstr "What are the performance differences between 24G radar and 10G radar?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/Rd/index.rst:80
#: b1c75b5a2bb546e185abe942c643ad5c
msgid "10g只能监测运动的人且没有距离信息，24g可以监测运动和静止的人体且有对应的距离信息"
msgstr ""
"10G radar can only detect moving people and does not provide distance "
"information. 24G radar can detect moving and stationary people and "
"provides corresponding distance information."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/Rd/index.rst:83
#: d211a35038a24c78a7fa99d8d8fa4341
msgid "请问RD-01的开发资料有么？"
msgstr "Are development materials available for RD-01?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/Rd/index.rst:84
#: afeaaebe5fd64827ad1b30d2a5bc8d2b
msgid "`官网  <https://docs.ai-thinker.com/rd-01>`__有，如下："
msgstr ""
"They are available on the `official website  <https://docs.ai-"
"thinker.com/rd-01>`__, as shown below:"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/Rd/index.rst:91
#: c4c3bb3c407147d38c0470c252b5bea0
msgid "请问Rd-03的数据帧是16进制的么？"
msgstr "Are the Rd-03 data frames in hexadecimal?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/Rd/index.rst:92
#: 498af7bc3f2f4d6e9647e371347aebc8
msgid "是的，每个字节数据均是hex数据；"
msgstr "Yes. Each byte of data is HEX data."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/Rd/index.rst:95
#: 11682a60a83e48cbabdb2122fab2cbe5
msgid "RD-01可以接入home assistaant吗"
msgstr "Can RD-01 be integrated with Home Assistant?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/Rd/index.rst:96
#: f3b2d98d3dfa4d04879a9d7285983aba
msgid "可以，不过需要做代码开发进行实现"
msgstr "Yes, but code development is required."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/Rd/index.rst:99
#: a8b4de88128446ddb4aa79b2521f63a4
msgid "RD-01模组最近距离是多少"
msgstr "What is the nearest detection distance of the RD-01 module?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/Rd/index.rst:100
#: d6f66194d1244c7b9abf50c08ece2069
msgid "一个距离门0.75m"
msgstr "One distance gate is 0.75 m."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/Rd/index.rst:103
#: 1534e61528784d3fa6ca05b9316a2af2
msgid "RD-03模组可以将波特率修改为9600吗"
msgstr "Can the baud rate of the Rd-03 module be changed to 9600?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/Rd/index.rst:104
#: ade9d7b3bf1a44abb73ebddb087dfa4a
msgid "可以，不过需要通过修改代码进行实现"
msgstr "Yes, but it must be implemented by modifying the code."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/Rd/index.rst:107
#: 4a63778ad9e9488bb40596ef7fff3b26
msgid "请问Rd-01是否支持platformio平台开发？"
msgstr "Does Rd-01 support development on the PlatformIO platform?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/Rd/index.rst:108
#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/Rd/index.rst:137
#: 3ac448f6e10442b1a2b6458289b17654 3c39fade79334aae88e64f749fa2be6f
msgid "不支持"
msgstr "Not supported."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/Rd/index.rst:111
#: 3e6ce2234f1641d2ba92e114b9a99183
